# ── Deliberately COMMITTED, despite looking like build output ───────────────────
#   src/sbomguard/static/ui/   the compiled dashboard. Committed on purpose: the
#                              project must run with no Node install and no CDN.
#   data/official/            the real SG sample data, so the evaluation and the
#                              data-defect proof are reproducible from a clean clone.
#   data/sample_data/         our reconstruction — the control that shows the engine
#                              scores 5/5 on internally-consistent data.
